Project Desktop3D

Description:

A project to make some cross platform 3D gadgets on your desktop for fun, joy and efficiency.

Technology:

Qt, OpenGL

Status:

Clock sample done.

Todo:

1. Grab the general parts from clock example, and put them into a library
2. Create more gadgets: theatre, bookshelf, news wall, weather window, album, mailbox, lava light, fish tank, forest, earth, butterfly, flags, running buddy (twitter), small house, plants, farm, train, fishing, etc.
